Uses of Package
org.gradoop.flink.util

  • Packages that use org.gradoop.flink.util 
    Package Description
    org.gradoop.examples.dimspan.data_source
    Optimized data source to use DIMSpan frequent subgraph mining standalone, i.e., not within Gradoop programs.
    org.gradoop.flink.algorithms.fsm.transactional.tle
    classes related to frequent subgraph mining
    org.gradoop.flink.algorithms.fsm.transactional.tle.functions
    Flink functions related to frequent subgraph mining.
    org.gradoop.flink.datagen.transactions.foodbroker
    Contains all classes related to FoodBroker.
    org.gradoop.flink.datagen.transactions.foodbroker.generators
    Contains all generator classes which generate master data objects used in FoodBroker.
    org.gradoop.flink.datagen.transactions.predictable
    contains classes for a predictable data generator for transactional frequent subgraph mining
    org.gradoop.flink.io.impl.csv
    Contains all classes related to CSV input and output to Flink.
    org.gradoop.flink.io.impl.csv.indexed
    Contains all classes related to indexed CSV input and output to Flink.
    org.gradoop.flink.io.impl.csv.metadata
    Contains all classes related to meta data used during CSV input and output to Flink.
    org.gradoop.flink.io.impl.deprecated.json
    Contains all classes related to json input and output to Flink.
    org.gradoop.flink.io.impl.deprecated.logicalgraphcsv
    Deprecated sources and necessary classes to read the old csv data.
    org.gradoop.flink.io.impl.edgelist
    Contains all classes related to graph data sources and data sinks.
    org.gradoop.flink.io.impl.graph
    Contains all classes related to reading an external graph into Gradoop.
    org.gradoop.flink.io.impl.tlf
    Contains all classes related to Transaction List Format (TLF) input and output to Flink.
    org.gradoop.flink.io.impl.tlf.functions
    Contains all Flink functions related to TLF input and output.
    org.gradoop.flink.model.api.epgm
    Contains interfaces for handling EPGM-structured graphs and graph collections.
    org.gradoop.flink.model.api.layouts
    Contains interfaces for describing graph and graph collection layouts.
    org.gradoop.flink.model.api.operators
    Contains all operator interface used in the Gradoop framework.
    org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.layouts.common
    Contains functionality that is used by all layout implementations.
    org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.grouping
    Contains all implementations of the graph grouping operator.
    org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.matching.common
    Contains functionality used by all pattern matching implementations.
    org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.transformation
    Contains the implementation of the graph modification operator.
    org.gradoop.flink.util
    Contains utility classes that are specific for the Flink implementations.
    org.gradoop.storage.impl.accumulo.io
    Contains accumulo store i/o classes for gradoop
    org.gradoop.storage.impl.hbase.io
    Contains all classes related to HBase input and output to and from Flink.
